sources.title: 1939 Zentrale Rio ( Leni Marenbach, Camilla Horn, Leo Peukert, Paul Hoffmann)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1939. Zentrale Rio.  U.a mit Leni Marenbach und Camilla Horn

metadata.Plot: Maria Halmborg is a widow. Her husband Erik - missing for years - is considered dead. Suddenly she learns that her husband allegedly lives in Rio and sets out on the journey to clarify the matter.
metadata.Writer: Rolf Dortenwald, Berthold Ebbecke, Ludwig Metzger
metadata.Actors: Leny Marenbach, Camilla Horn, Ita Rina
